criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  All students aged 10-19 years enrolled in the College Presidente Emilio Garrastazu
             Medici (Currently its name is College Estadual do Stiep Carlos Marighella) whose
             present the Statement of Consent Form signed by parents/ tutors and by themselves;

          -  Individuals of the same age with symptoms suggestive of asthma and/or previous
             diagnosis as well as those without asthma after signing the Statement of Consent Form
             may be included;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Individuals not willing to participate of the study;

          -  Individuals who have not signed the consent form;

          -  Individuals with cognitive impairment and with any special needs must not be included
             in this study.
